A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the Jonesboro Majestic Marching Cardinals; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Jonesboro Majestic Marching Cardinals is an esteemed musical ensemble
4 dedicated to taking learning beyond the classroom, providing students with access to
5 invaluable experiences and once-in-a-lifetime opportunities through music; and
6 WHEREAS, the band strives to prepare students for post-secondary education by offering
7 exposure to diverse opportunities through travel and assisting graduating seniors in securing
8 music scholarships, thereby making higher education more accessible and affordable; and
9 WHEREAS, the Jonesboro Majestic Marching Cardinals have established themselves as the
10 premier ambassadors for Clayton County and the Jonesboro community; and
11 WHEREAS, under the leadership of Director Lynel Goodwin, the band has earned national
12 acclaim through major accomplishments such as performing at the City of Jonesboro
13 Mayoral Inauguration in 2019, participating in the nationally televised Chicago Thanksgiving
14 Day Parade in 2019, making an appearance on Good Morning America in 2021, and
15 emerging as champions of the Great Atlanta Band Challenge in 2021; and
